Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都會變得愈加沉悶炎熱的這個暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真要是說日本列島正在熱帶化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概沒那種可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓我揮之不去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大可能是起因於我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位長門和我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共度了步入夏季之前的那段短暫時光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把自己想說的都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且沒有留給我回答的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那樣消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在意起那個時候的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對現在的長門就開不了口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後總覺得有些不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個意…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有及時注意到 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓長門難堪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假已經過了一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用富士山來打比方的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是在半山腰的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去山腰的話好像只需要坐車就能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裏開始才算是真正的登山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以現在的心境來看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也感覺不到暑假正值盛期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點justly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在咖啡店集合over
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也做過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是之前在社團教室裏說過的計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要在這個夏天之內做完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個需要在下周完成 古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個夏天真是夠忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是富士山的話大概在半山腰的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 竟然會和這傢伙有同樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說現在開始才是真正的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高二的暑假只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在盡情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒有玩夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅只有一次的暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下起雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼宮 帶傘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是涼宮 準備周全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到車站前集合 別遲到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說有雨之日的促銷活動 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有帶傘過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是會不自覺的在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法正常的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨 停了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的螢火蟲一樣漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假才過去一半
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有剩下的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該做些行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是箱斷之之後我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像瞬間被吃掉的蕎麥面一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不跟著涼宮制定的計劃過日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉眼間時間就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了 全壘打 全壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情緒跟打數一樣高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有精神的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 下一發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是真的熱血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈學姐 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 揮動的太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再稍微把棒球棒握短一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是說出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 明明就有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全倒 耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是朝全中去的 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後我和長門之間沒有什麼對話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假就這樣快過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別灰心 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重振精神再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 長門 現在才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多挽回的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是說出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 下一個是阿虛你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣根本算不上在比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 涼宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個缺口可以算是很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 說到底都是幹勁的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太用力 自然一點扔出去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定能取得好結果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你能說出這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅限於保齡球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過於在意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而會偏離目標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定這種情況很常見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把北高隊伍完全比下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶 漂亮的全倒 做的真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慚愧慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在疲於奔波中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假也漸漸過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動也僅剩下一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是當地的小祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻相當熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為日本人喜歡祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已經在買東西吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡祭典的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了啊 真遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上這個可費了不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服會起皺折的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位都很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算是夏日風情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 浴衣是跟鶴屋學姐借的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起一般的小店 品種豐富得多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實她說要送給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是涼子卻拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種布料在普通商場可買不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是在擔心能不能不弄髒的還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想的真多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鶴屋學姐和朝比奈學姐去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實物示範？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上確實有那種攤子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在賣連手機都能粉碎的攪拌機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人很容易著迷於郵購推銷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鶴屋學姐的苦笑可是難得一見喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 她叫我們先出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說讓我們先隨意逛逛夜店是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 涼宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛說完就這樣 會起皺折的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,300日元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 給我牢固的網
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼子 幫我擺頭髮 快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當初穿衣服的時候不是說不用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候是因為太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買糖葫蘆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 有希 別發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來比賽 看誰撈的金魚最多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想想方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就開始救你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好孩子 別亂動喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛 要看準金魚的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準目標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還能再抓上20條
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你看來我肯定是個優柔寡斷的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使知道前段時間的長門跟現在的長門不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的感情也不是那麼簡單就能弄懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的長門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很明白自己在不知明的狀況下被你疏離了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很抱歉 沒能馬上反應過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該早就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到尷尬的不止是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門也是 因為我的行為而難受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是時候表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候 沒能說出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟我來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下來要玩射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的 被你表白的時候我一下子沒能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不覺得自己有做出讓你想告白的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？你說什麼？我沒聽見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說我哪裏好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 給我聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會討厭長門的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 表白的回復 只能是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定早就喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛說的 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 這就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 緊張死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對 你那反應也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不好意思 前段時間那麼冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說有點強硬 但能說出心裏話 真舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始就是平常的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了 去吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊我也餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃什麼 我請你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別介意 反正春日會隨便找個理由讓我請客的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 那浴衣很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想要別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有我的許可就離群
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 做為懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家吃章魚燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈學姐那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的最後久違的社團後回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然發現了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是夏日集訓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果卻去了海邊游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山裏的試膽大冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市民游泳池裏的玩樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天體觀測
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩了保齡球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有擊球中心跟夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像樣的文學活動一個都沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我想在文化祭裏出個小冊子或是接力小說什麼的 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 完全就是文化社了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們 連這個都忘記了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑 開玩笑了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟涼宮說了的話感覺她會幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫出來的肯定會有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異界人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超能者等一次跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 感覺好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 要試著寫小說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去長門家一起吃飯怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意 就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提 有什麼菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關東煮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,summer關東煮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼熱的天吃關東煮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想搞忍耐大賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日裏吃關東煮 別有一番風味喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 要變紅燈了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點羞澀的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門有希的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思議的這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 你有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 你今天很閒對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我兩點整在咖啡店裏集合 over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.44,0:24:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作業做好了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊

